      "duration_frames": 241,
      "duration_seconds": 10.042,
      "timeline_data": "{\"segments\":[{\"id\":\"1781658567266y9yfz\",\"start\":0,\"length\":48,\"prompt\":\"Shot 1 (Full Shot, 1.84s):  environment remains completely unchanged.\\nAction: In slow-motion, Minh slowly blinks, his breathing barely perceptible. Smooth and fluid movement throughout.\\nShot 2 (Full Shot, 1.84s):  environment remains completely unchanged.\\nAction: He gently shifts his weight forward, a subtle, fluid motion through his shoulders and hips.\\nShot 3 (Full Shot, 1.83s): environment remains completely unchanged.\\nAction: His head turns an almost imperceptible degree to the side, his eyes following a path through the rain. Subtle, deep, contemplative.\",\"type\":\"image\",\"imageFile\":\"m_5d8fdcf9937101269d596e2bf94a990f96ad9d69.webp\",\"imageB64\":\"/api/view?filename=m_5d8fdcf9937101269d596e2bf94a990f96ad9d69.webp&type=input&subfolder=\"},{\"id\":\"17816585747457ddrc\",\"start\":48,\"length\":48,\"prompt\":\" Minh gently shakes his head from side to side with soft, fluid motion, while exhaling quietly through his nose, his raised eyebrow gradually lowering back to a neutral position.\",\"type\":\"image\",\"imageFile\":\"m_417157bd2bbbdd96c599191deef75c3008beb51b.webp\",\"imageB64\":\"/api/view?filename=m_417157bd2bbbdd96c599191deef75c3008beb51b.webp&type=input&subfolder=\"},{\"id\":\"1781658581081p2xqq\",\"start\":96,\"length\":73,\"prompt\":\"Linh holds an umbrella for Minh. Lip Linh finished the last syllable of the question, the folded umbrella was held firmly, a gentle smile slowly appeared on her lips. Minh's eyes slid down to the umbrella and then looked up at her face, his expression changed from slightly surprised to quietly admitting.\\n\\n\",\"type\":\"image\",\"imageFile\":\"m_0b21ff622bf5d1e4112f23e8d4f42d3cec73ac81.webp\",\"imageB64\":\"/api/view?filename=m_0b21ff622bf5d1e4112f23e8d4f42d3cec73ac81.webp&type=input&subfolder=\"},{\"id\":\"1781659642704tp3gx\",\"start\":169,\"length\":31,\"prompt\":\"Shot 1 (Over-the-Shoulder Medium Shot, 0.88s): Static camera, environment remains unchanged.\\nMinh: \\\"Yours?\\\"\\nAction: In slow-motion, Minh's lips gently close and press together briefly, then part again as he speaks the words, his gaze remaining locked on hers. A soft, subtle shift of his eyebrow and a single slow blink accompany the question. Smooth and fluid micro-movement.\",\"type\":\"image\",\"imageFile\":\"m_f69cd3b11af99681a7085fadd4e8d4476df2db60.webp\",\"imageB64\":\"/api/view?filename=m_f69cd3b11af99681a7085fadd4e8d4476df2db60.webp&type=input&subfolder=\"},{\"id\":\"17816596598150far7\",\"start\":200,\"length\":41,\"prompt\":\"Shot 1 (Medium Shot, 1.33s): Static camera, environment remains unchanged.\\nLinh: \\\"I have two.\\\"\\nAction: Slow-motion. Linh's lips part as she speaks the line, her smile subtly widening; Minh's eyes shift slightly down and back up, a micro-nod. All movement is smooth and fluid. No camera movement.\",\"type\":\"image\",\"imageFile\":\"m_5ea1f53c3329ca39048f53d3d77cb4300e377a5f.webp\",\"imageB64\":\"/api/view?filename=m_5ea1f53c3329ca39048f53d3d77cb4300e377a5f.webp&type=input&subfolder=\"}],\"audioSegments\":[{\"id\":\"1781660353232okrml\",\"type\":\"audio\",\"start\":0,\"length\":109,\"trimStart\":0,\"audioDurationFrames\":109,\"audioFile\":\"nam_manh_dung.wav\",\"fileName\":\"nam_manh_dung.wav\",\"waveformPeaks\":[0.08492860943078995,0.4754074811935425,0.4443306028842926,0.41995298862457275,0.3808736503124237,0.2891766428947449,0.2620111405849457,0.21786046028137207,0.41196346282958984,0.38534578680992126,0.39140230417251587,0.27544960379600525,0.445485383272171,0.46778276562690735,0.4189388155937195,0.26120585203170776,0.0215156227350235,0.0038777075242251158,0.004608402028679848,0.009841863997280598,0.46235090494155884,0.45798781514167786,0.21635937690734863,0.15019908547401428,0.11672908812761307,0.0881342664361,0.1283295452594757,0.2916017174720764,0.32203447818756104,0.32829201221466064,0.3147434592247009,0.19976061582565308,0.212988242506980