      "local_prompts": "Shot 1 (Full Shot, 1.84s):  environment remains completely unchanged.\nAction: In slow-motion, Minh slowly blinks, his breathing barely perceptible. Smooth and fluid movement throughout.\nShot 2 (Full Shot, 1.84s):  environment remains completely unchanged.\nAction: He gently shifts his weight forward, a subtle, fluid motion through his shoulders and hips.\nShot 3 (Full Shot, 1.83s): environment remains completely unchanged.\nAction: His head turns an almost imperceptible degree to the side, his eyes following a path through the rain. Subtle, deep, contemplative. |  Minh gently shakes his head from side to side with soft, fluid motion, while exhaling quietly through his nose, his raised eyebrow gradually lowering back to a neutral position. | Linh holds an umbrella for Minh. Lip Linh finished the last syllable of the question, the folded umbrella was held firmly, a gentle smile slowly appeared on her lips. Minh's eyes slid down to the umbrella and then looked up at her face, his expression changed from slightly surprised to quietly admitting.\n\n | Shot 1 (Over-the-Shoulder Medium Shot, 0.88s): Static camera, environment remains unchanged.\nMinh: \"Yours?\"\nAction: In slow-motion, Minh's lips gently close and press together briefly, then part again as he speaks the words, his gaze remaining locked on hers. A soft, subtle shift of his eyebrow and a single slow blink accompany the question. Smooth and fluid micro-movement. | Shot 1 (Medium Shot, 1.33s): Static camera, environment remains unchanged.\nLinh: \"I have two.\"\nAction: Slow-motion. Linh's lips part as she speaks the line, her smile subtly widening; Minh's eyes shift slightly down and back up, a micro-nod. All movement is smooth and fluid. No camera movement.",
